data.description: OR BETTER OFFER!  HEAR YE! HEAR YE!      This townhome may be leased immediately after closing so if you're looking to make passive RENTAL INCOME or occupy it as your primary residence, look no further... here’s your opportunity to own in the highly sought after and fully gated community of Edgewater at Lake Brandon.    This fabulously cozy - END UNIT - two-story townhome is packed with awesome features:    •Taexx - the original Tubes in the Wall system.    •A flex room that can easily double as an office space or den.    •Spacious family room and dinette with faux-wood luxury vinyl flooring.    •The kitchen comes fully equipped with Corian countertops, canned ceiling lighting, a spacious breakfast bar, closet pantry, and all appliances: refrigerator, stove, mounted microwave, dishwasher.    •A guest bathroom on the first floor includes ceramic tile and a pedestal sink.    •The second level houses the carpeted master bedroom which includes a walk-in closet, its own private bathroom featuring a walk-in shower and a water closet.    •The laundry closet is conveniently located on the second floor by the bedrooms and stocked with ventilated shelving, lighting, and full-size side-by-side washer and dryer.    •Both carpeted guest bedrooms are also on the second floor, each equipped with ceiling fans and built-in closets.    •The attached one car garage includes an automatic remote door opener.    •NON-FLOOD ZONE X.    This quaint and fully gated community is just minutes from public transportation, major highways, shopping centers, restaurants, and local entertainment.    With HOA dues of just $290 per month – which covers your water bill and roof maintenance – makes this property an incredible investment so don’t miss out on this home and schedule your showing today!
